图片来源：视觉中国“ 目前，黎某正在定点医院接受治疗，其丈夫、儿子接受隔离观察。
Photo Source: Vision China "Currently, Li Mou is receiving treatment at a designated hospital and her husband and son are under quarantine observation.
”因登机后未如实提供个人情况，北京一例从美国输入的确诊病例被警方以涉嫌妨害传染病防治罪立案侦查。
A confirmed case imported from the US has been investigated by the police on suspicion of obstructing the control of infectious diseases for failing to provide true personal details after boarding the plane.
2020年3月16日，@平安北京通报，3月13日，本市报告1例从美国输入的确诊病例，黎某，女，37岁，长期定居美国马萨诸塞州。
16 March 2020, @ Ping An Beijing informed that, on March 13, the city reported a confirmed case imported from the United States. Le Mou, a 37-year-old woman, had settled permanently in Massachusetts, USA.
3月14、15日，市疾控中心和中国国际航空公司在北京市新冠肺炎疫情防控工作新闻发布会上通报，黎某在美期间已出现发热、咳嗽等症状，并多次在当地就诊，在美国登机前曾服用退烧药，登机后未如实向乘务人员提供个人健康状况及丈夫、儿子等同行人员情况，给同机人员造成传染风险。
On March 14 and 15, the CDC and Air China reported at a press conference that Li had developed fever, cough and other symptoms during his stay in the United States.
通报称，接相关线索后，北京警方迅速开展调查取证。
The notice said that after receiving the relevant clues, Beijing police quickly conducted an investigation to collect evidence.
经初步工作，顺义公安分局以涉嫌妨害传染病防治罪，已对黎某立案侦查。
After preliminary work, Shunyi Public Security Bureau on suspicion of obstructing the prevention and control of infectious diseases, a case has been opened against Lebanon.
目前，黎某正在定点医院接受治疗，其丈夫、儿子接受隔离观察。
Currently, Le Mou is receiving treatment at the designated hospital, her husband and son are under quarantine observation.
此前在3月14日，北京市疾控中心在新闻发布会上通报黎某相关情况时表示，黎某自述2月26日至27日在美国参加公司会议，其中一同事后来被诊断为确诊病例。
Earlier, on March 14, Beijing CDC reported at a news conference that Li had attended a company meeting in the United States from February 26 to 27, and one of his colleagues was later diagnosed as a confirmed case.
3月1日晚，黎某出现发热等相关症状。
March 1 night, Lebanon appeared fever and other related symptoms.
而后，黎某在美国3次申请核酸检测均被拒绝。
Later, Lebanon in the United States three applications for nucleic acid testing were rejected.
为进一步诊治，黎某及其丈夫、儿子一家三口乘机回国。
To further diagnosis and treatment, Le Mou, her husband, the family of three flew home.
对此，在北京市3月15日举行的新闻发布会上，国航相关负责人表示，3月12日，黎某在航班起飞后，找到乘务员，自称感到憋气、乏力、脸部微麻，并说自己没有同行者，且登机前未服用过任何药品，但一周前有短暂的发烧史。
In response, Air China officials said at a press conference on March 15 that Li had found a flight attendant on March 12 who said he was suffocating, fatigued and had no facial numbness. He said he had no companions and had not taken any medicine before boarding, but had a short fever a week ago.
乘务组将其调整到客舱右后部留观隔离区就坐，但在航班落地前两小时，黎某找到乘务员，称自己在美国任职公司有人感染，自己在美国已经发烧，并在登机前吃了退烧药，丈夫和孩子也同机旅行。
The crew adjusted it to the rear right of the cabin and sat in the quarantine zone. But two hours before the flight landed, Le Mou found a flight attendant who claimed to be an employee of the United States. He had a fever in the United States.
乘务组立即将此情况报告，国航运控中心接到报告后立刻通知相关部门，启动联防联控机制。
The crew immediately reported the situation to the national shipping control centre, which immediately notified the relevant departments to activate the joint control mechanism.
@平安北京表示，当前境外疫情加速扩散蔓延，防范境外疫情输入是防控工作的重中之重，所有入境进京人员应严格遵守相关法律及疫情防控相关规定。
@ Ping An Beijing said the current spread of the epidemic abroad accelerated, prevention of the importation of foreign epidemic disease is a top priority, all incoming personnel should strictly abide by the relevant laws and regulations on disease prevention and control.
对虚报信息、隐瞒病情等拒绝执行疫情防控措施的违法犯罪行为，北京警方将坚决打击处理、依法追究责任。
The Beijing police will resolutely crack down on, and investigate the responsibility for, any illegal or criminal act of refusing to carry out epidemic prevention and control measures by misrepresenting information and concealing illness.
